    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Prepare to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and performing exactly as it did when it first hit the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, making it the perfect choice for a buyer who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
