      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to a concours standard. This specimen represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation, featuring an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Meticulously serviced and strictly garaged, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly pristine example of the marque. Its mechanical performance remains as sharp as the day it left the assembly line, ensuring an unparalleled driving experience for its next steward.",
      "price": 48500.0,
